  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Game!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/5090db98d4dc891961a3a45574a0c54c.avif?t=1771997806\" width=462 height=174 /></span><br>Please scroll down to MORE FROM RENKA!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>You will play as a deliveryman and encounter various characters and events. You need to make your own judgments and choices.<br>After that, your attributes will change according to the outcomes of your choices.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/96427a87b8cabe6efe2abac2aa58b66c.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><br>When your attributes drop to zero or go too high, you will meet a bad ending or something special.<br>The attributes will change slowly over time to prepare you for the incoming accidents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/c5e438a52ae4e68afc5abd4d8a94365b.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><br>For example, you can give up the current event and let another personality take your place to handle all the problems for you.<br>In this situation, the current event and changes to your attributes will be interrupted.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/32acbf7e0b6ca51a1ae485653c643aa3.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><br>Quitting an event comes with a price. Your attributes will decline after giving up events but your level will rise instead.<br>Your level may play an essential role  on certain occasions and determine the course of events.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/971fd443cdefb3acec8d84a083bdd671.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><br>On Day 30, something will happen and you may reach the end or go back to the first day.<br>Anyway, the fate of the characters depends on your choices.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.poster.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.webm?t=1771997806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.mp4?t=1771997806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "You will play as a deliveryman and encounter various characters and events. You need to make your own judgments and choices.<br>After that, your attributes will change according to the outcomes of your choices.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/96427a87b8cabe6efe2abac2aa58b66c.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><br>When your attributes drop to zero or go too high, you will meet a bad ending or something special.<br>The attributes will change slowly over time to prepare you for the incoming accidents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/c5e438a52ae4e68afc5abd4d8a94365b.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><br>For example, you can give up the current event and let another personality take your place to handle all the problems for you.<br>In this situation, the current event and changes to your attributes will be interrupted.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/32acbf7e0b6ca51a1ae485653c643aa3.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><br>Quitting an event comes with a price. Your attributes will decline after giving up events but your level will rise instead.<br>Your level may play an essential role  on certain occasions and determine the course of events.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/971fd443cdefb3acec8d84a083bdd671.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><br>On Day 30, something will happen and you may reach the end or go back to the first day.<br>Anyway, the fate of the characters depends on your choices.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.poster.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.webm?t=1771997806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.mp4?t=1771997806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
